posting_body: ['The Pacifica', '4275 South Pine Street, Tacoma, WA, 98409', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 25', 'OR Text', '25', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Welcome Home to The Pacifica $1514 - STUDIO home for IMMEDIATE move in!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1160 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Pacifica is one of the newest premier luxury apartments in Tacoma, Washington.', 'Offering the latest amenities in apartment living like a resort-style swimming pool and an amazing clubhouse, these apartments offer the best in world class Northwest living.', 'Close to Seattle, these apartments feature full-size washers and dryers, stainless steel appliance packages, walk-in closets, granite counter tops, and two custom-designed interior finishes to choose from.', 'The Pacifica gives you unmatched access to shopping, dining, entertainment, Sound Transit, freeways, and is just minutes away from Joint Base Lewis McChord.', 'Contact us today and Say', 'Yes, to The Pacifica.', 'Features', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Full-Size Washer/Dryer', '- Walk-In Closets', '- Private Patio or Balcony', '- Granite Countertops', '- 2 Custom-Designed Interior Finishes', 'Community Amenities', '- Garage Parking Access: $95.00', '- Clubhouse', '- Gated Parking Access: $60.00', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', '- Fitness Center', '- Resort-Style Swimming Pool', '- Business Center', '- Controlled Access/Gated', '*ASSIGNED PARKING AVAILABILITY*', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, contact for details.', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '9HPprPE32d']
